dialogList.content: (It looks like there may have been a fight here, but it's hard to say for certain.)
(This was the work of a professional... but who?)
(A fresh fruit pit. Someone was here recently.)
(There don't seem to be any more clues.)
(These stripes in the dirt were likely made by a bamboo mat. That means someone slept here.)
(But the bamboo mat is nowhere to be seen now.)
